      "factId": "hz.web.c84a1aed984224ed.fact.1",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "The California Online Privacy Protection Act (CalOPPA) | Consumer Federation of California Education Foundation Consumer Federation of California California Online Privacy Protection Act (CalOPPA) —updated July 29, 2015 The first state law in the nation to require commercial websites and online services to post a privacy policy, the California Online Privacy Protection Act (CalOPPA) went into effect in 2004.",
