      "factId": "hz.web.c84a1aed984224ed.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "CalOPPA requires the website to feature a conspicuous privacy policy stating exactly what information is collected and with whom it is shared; it also requires the operator of the website or online service to comply with the site’s privacy policy.",
